Moodle block littlestar

Author: Max Kan max_kan@hotmail.com

Feature:
1. allow course participants rate course/resources/activities
2. AJAX
3. rating can be exported

***************************************************************************

    Ajax rating works based on 'Ajax-PHP Rating Stars Script'
    from 'CourseWeb programming'

    http://coursesweb.net/php-mysql/rating-stars-script-ajax-php_s2

***************************************************************************

Installation:
1. Copy folder Moodle-block_littlestar to <MOODLE_HOME>/block/littlestar
2. Login Moodle as Admin
3. Run Notifications

User guide:
1. Teacher add the block to the course
2. Configure the block instance, swith the 'Display on page types' to 'Any page' in order
    to allow the block appear in resource/activity page